  4803→	// and whether deleting it would lockout the user from login.
  4804→	//
  4805→	// Note: the user may already be locked out from login if a password
  4806→	// is not set and passwordless is disabled. Prevent them from deleting
  4807→	// their last passkey to prevent them from being locked out further,
